cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D human pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel feature representation and uses regression networks, which are common in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves reasoning and decision-making, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. The paper also involves graphics and visualization, which suggests cs.GR (Graphics) as another possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of datasets, which suggests cs.MM (Multimedia) as another possible category.
